column2: select p.objid, p.g, p.r, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux from GalSpecLine as g join photoObj as p ON p.specobjid = g.specobjid join dbo.fGetObjFromRectEq(#, #, #, #) n on p.objid=n.objid join specObj s on p.objid=s.bestobjid where p.petrorad_r > # and p.r < # and s.Class= &&& and s.z >= #
